item.description:
We want to increase the size of the legend keys and split the legend over 3 columns, of a ggplot object called p.
Code By expliciting the package name:
#!/usr/bin/R p + ggplot2::guides(color = ggplot2::guide_legend(override.aes = list(size = 5), ncol = 3)) Without the package name:
#!/usr/bin/R library(ggplot2) p + guides(color = guide_legend(override.aes = list(size = 5), ncol = 3))
